{"id":118,"date":"2016-01-26T07:12:41","date_gmt":"2016-01-26T07:12:41","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/cascadeskischool.com\/wordpress\/?page_id=118"},"modified":"2023-10-01T06:53:51","modified_gmt":"2023-10-01T06:53:51","slug":"classes-2","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/cascadeskischool.com\/classes-2\/","title":{"rendered":"Classes"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'arial black', sans-serif;\"><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/cascadeskischool.com\/saturday-ski-and-snowboard-lessons\/\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">SATURDAY Ski and Snowboard Classes<\/span><\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'arial black', sans-serif;\"><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/cascadeskischool.com\/sunday-ski-snowboard-lessons\/\">SUNDAY Ski Classes<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h5><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>Participation Agreement:<\/strong><\/span><\/h5>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Enrollment deadline <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">December 1, 2023<\/span>. \u00a0Applications accepted after deadline<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">on space-available basis.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">I accept my responsibility to ski safely at all time, to abide by the skier&#8217;s<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Responsibility Code, now titled &#8220;Your Responsibility Code&#8221; and to obey all posted<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">behavior notices and other ski area rules and policies.<\/span><\/p>\n<h5><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Since all instruction is reserved for entire season, there are no\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">refunds or make-up lessons if a student misses a class.<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h5>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">There may be unforeseen circumstances or conditions which will force the ski\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">school to postpone or cancel a session or sessions.<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">In the event of postponement, make-up lessons will be scheduled and the\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">ski\/snowboard\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">season will automatically be extended until ALL lessons are completed.<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Plan\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">for an extended ski\/snowboard season if we should get a late start or have any\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><\/span><strong style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">interruptions\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><strong style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">in our schedule.<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">If we are forced to cancel and the program is not completed, we will refund tuition\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">fees less the number of weeks ski school operated. A $25 administration fee will\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">be charged to issue a refund for any reason.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">TUITION does not include lift tickets, ski equipment, clothing or lunch. Lessons\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">are not transferable.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">MEDICAL INSURANCE: All students are required to have medical or accident\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">insurance which covers skiing.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">There are hazards involved in the sport of skiing and snowboarding, as in\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">all active sports, and accidents may happen.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">CONFIRMATION: Upon receipt of entire signed registration form and\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">fees, detailed ski school information will be mailed or emailed which\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">will include:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">-Ski area and ski school information<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">-Equipment and clothing tips<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">-Application for season pass if requested (early registration is necessary)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Please Note: No classes will be held on<\/span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">\u00a0President\u2019s Day\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Weekend.<\/span><\/p>\n<h5><a href=\"https:\/\/cascadeskischool.com\/enrollment\/\">Enrollment Page<\/a><\/h5>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp; SATURDAY Ski and Snowboard Classes SUNDAY Ski Classes &nbsp; Participation Agreement: Enrollment deadline December 1, 2023. \u00a0Applications accepted after deadline on space-available basis. I accept my responsibility to ski <a href=\"https:\/\/cascadeskischool.com\/classes-2\/\" class=\"more-link\">[&hellip;]<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"Layout":"","footnotes":""},"class_list":["entry","author-admin","post-118","page","type-page","status-publish"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/cascadeskischool.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/118","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/cascadeskischool.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/cascadeskischool.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/cascadeskischool.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/cascadeskischool.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=118"}],"version-history":[{"count":28,"href":"https:\/\/cascadeskischool.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/118\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":680,"href":"https:\/\/cascadeskischool.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/118\/revisions\/680"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/cascadeskischool.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=118"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}